\c 11
\s Ataria mai vaAhazia, anobata ushe hwaJudha
\p
\v 1 Zvino Ataria mai vaAhazia paakaona kuti mwanakomana wake wafa, wakasimuka ndokuparadza mbeu yese yamambo.
\v 2 Asi Jehoshebha mukunda wamambo Joramu, hanzvadzi yaAhazia, wakatora Joashi mwanakomana waAhazia, ndokumuba kubva pakati pevanakomana vamambo vaiurawa, iye nemureri wake mukamuri yekurarara. Zvino vakamuviga pachiso chaAtaria kuti asaurawa.
\v 3 Zvino waiva naye muimba yaJehovha makore matanhatu; Ataria ndokutonga pamusoro penyika.
\p
\v 4 Zvino negore rechinomwe Jehoyadha wakatuma \add nhume \add*ndokutora misoro yemazana, \add \add*yevaKari neyevarindi, ndokuiunza kwaari muimba yaJehovha, ndokuita sungano navo, ndokuvapikisa muimba yaJehovha, ndokuvaratidza mwanakomana wamambo.
\v 5 Zvino wakavaraira achiti: Ichi chinhu chamunofanira kuita: Chetatu chenyu chinopinda nesabata chichava varindi vechirindo cheimba yamambo,
\v 6 uye chetatu chichava pasuwo reSuri; uye chetatu pasuwo shure kwevarindi; saizvozvo muchachengeta chirindo cheimba, isapaziwa.
\v 7 Zvino mapoka enyu maviri, imwi mese munobuda nesabata, munofanira kurinda imba yaJehovha muchikomba mambo.
\v 8 Mukombe mambo, umwe neumwe akabata nhumbi dzokurwa nadzo muruoko rwake; ani nani unopinda pakati pemisara, unofanira kuurawa; mugare namambo kana achibuda uye kana achipinda.
\v 9 Vakuru vamazana vakaita zvese zvavakarairwa nomupristi Jehoyadha; umwe neumwe akatora vanhu vake, ivo vaifanira kupinda nesabata, naivo vaifanira kubuda nesabata, vakasvika kumupristi Jehoyadha.
\v 10 Mupristi akapa vakuru vamazana mapfumo nenhowo zvaiva zvamambo Dhavhidhi, zvakange zviri mumba maJehovha.
\v 11 Zvino varindi vamambo vakamira umwe neumwe akabata nhumbi dzokurwa nadzo muruoko rwake, kubva kurutivi rworudyi rweimba kusvikira kurutivi rworuboshwe rweimba, napaaritari neimba, vakakomba mambo.
\v 12 Ipapo akabudisa mwanakomana wamambo, akamudzika korona, akamupa chipupuriro, vakamuita mambo, vakamuzodza; ndokuridza nhondo, vachiti: Mambo ngaararame!
\p
\v 13 Zvino Ataria wakati achinzwa mhere-mhere yavarindi vamambo navanhu, akapinda kuvanhu mumba maJehovha.
\v 14 Akatarira, ndokuona mambo amire pambiru, netsika yavo, navakuru navakange vane hwamanda vamire kuna mambo; vanhu vese venyika vakafara, vakaridza hwamanda. Ipapo Ataria akabvarura nguvo dzake, akadanidzira, achiti: Ndamukirwa, ndamukirwa!
\v 15 Zvino mupristi Jehoyadha akaraira vakuru vamazana, vairaira hondo, akati kwavari: Mubudisei pakati pemisara yavanhu; ani nani unomutevera iye, munofanira kumuuraya nomunondo; nokuti mupristi wakati: Ngaarege kuurayiwa mukati meimba yaJehovha.
\v 16 Naizvozvo vakamubata namaoko, akaenda nenzira yaipinda mabhiza nayo kumba kwamambo, ndokuurayirwapo.
\p
\v 17 Zvino Jehoyadha akaita sungano pakati paJehovha namambo navanhu, kuti vave vanhu vaJehovha; uyewo pakati pamambo navanhu.
\v 18 Vanhu vese venyika vakaenda kumba kwaBhaari, vakaiputsa; vakaputsa kwazvo aritari dzake nemifananidzo yake, vakauraya Matani mupristi waBhaari pamberi pearitari. Mupristi akagadza vatariri paimba yaJehovha.
\v 19 Akatora vakuru vamazana, navaKari, navarindi vamambo, navanhu vese venyika, vakaburusa mambo paimba yaJehovha, vakaenda kumba kwamambo nenzira yesuwo ravarindi vamambo. Iye akagara pachigaro choushe chamadzimambo.
\v 20 Naizvozvo vanhu vese venyika vakafara, guta rikanyarara; vakauraya Ataria nomunondo paimba yamambo.
\v 21 Jehoashi wakatanga kubata ushe ari wemakore manomwe.
